{"tid":572523,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Kickstarter世界評議會2被走數苦主集合區","createTime":"2018-02-25T15:52:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-27T03:44:56.000Z","uid":134019,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ecac2ed24303ff2da2c9860d8370f79078e21df8","tid":572523,"uid":134019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T15:52:51.000Z","msg":"事緣係有間公司Creator studio 搞左個boardgame，the world council，本身第一版都好好玩，雖然係遲左小小出貨但起碼最尾都收到，都好好玩<br />\n<br />\n咁之後出個擴充包2，見都幾吸引，就支持埋back啦，點知成功fund完之後就無哂聲氣，追一輪又話delay印刷，再追又話可以refund，由17年9月成功fund到而家就3月都差唔多成半年，錢又無退到，又唔知progress係點(最緊要係一路係到宣傳緊其他boardgame，整新野)<br />\n<br />\n而家kickstarter個邊個個backer都屌哂鬼，想問有無連登仔都back左？"},{"pid":"60b7988dadf52bd2e24d265f19e880708f2368f9","tid":572523,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T15:53:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8028ba947f47d7f4fea448fe730a66b1c3e1303e","tid":572523,"uid":134019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T15:54:59.000Z","msg":"The World Council 2 - A Board Game For Summit, via @Kickstarter <a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1723848355/the-world-council-second-print-with-future-council\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kickstarter.com%2Fprojects%2F1723848355%2Fthe-world-council-second-print-with-future-council&d=0aXBO8R3NAgxOxur3ej%2FIqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=603fac58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1723848355/the-world-council-second-print-with-future-council</a>"},{"pid":"250790cf852070fe398546cbc099483c22dea27e","tid":572523,"uid":134019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8028ba947f47d7f4fea448fe730a66b1c3e1303e","tid":572523,"uid":134019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T15:54:59.000Z","msg":"The World Council 2 - A Board Game For Summit, via @Kickstarter <a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1723848355/the-world-council-second-print-with-future-c